        <briefdescription>
<para>Full/sequentially-consistent data memory barrier across cores. </para>
        </briefdescription>
        <detaileddescription>
<para>This routine acts as a synchronization fence between threads/cores and prevents re-ordering of data accesses instructions across the barrier instruction. </para>
        </detaileddescription>
